Structure your summary:
1. **Overview**: One-paragraph high-level summary
2. **Key Points**: The most important information (bulleted)
3. **Decisions Made**: Any decisions or conclusions reached
4. **Action Items**: What needs to happen next (if applicable)
5. **Open Questions**: What remains unresolved (if applicable)

Length: ~20% of original unless otherwise specified.
